rdf:Description.Label: Select Query Rendered as a Grid
Explore an instance of a selected node type
What are the shared services budget items?
What line items does this system have for this year?
What enterprise line items exist below this tag?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT ?sys ?budget ?value ?gltag1 (COALESCE(?gltag2, '') AS ?GLtag2) (COALESCE(?gltag3, '') AS ?GLtag3) WHERE { {?sys <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/System> ;} {?budget <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemBudgetGLItem> ;}{?has <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Has>;} {?sys ?has ?budget .}{?budget <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/OldPrositeCost> ?value ;} BIND(<@Tag-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag@> AS ?gltag1){ {?tagged1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TaggedBy> ;} {?budget ?tagged1 ?gltag1 ;} }UNION{{?contains <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?gltag2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?gltag1 ?contains ?gltag2 ;} {?tagged1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TaggedBy> ;} {?budget ?tagged1 ?gltag2 ;}} UNION {{?gltag3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?contains2 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?gltag2 ?contains2 ?gltag3;}{?contains <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?gltag2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?gltag1 ?contains ?gltag2 ;} {?tagged1 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TaggedBy> ;} {?budget ?tagged1 ?gltag3 ;}}}

rdf:Description.Label: What tags exist below this tag?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT (?tag1 AS ?Tag1) (IF(BOUND(?tag2), ?tag2, '') AS ?Tag2) (IF(BOUND(?tag3), ?tag3, '') AS ?Tag3) (IF(BOUND(?tag4), ?tag4, '') AS ?Tag4) WHERE { BIND(<@Tag-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag@> AS ?tag1) OPTIONAL { {?contains <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?tag2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?tag1 ?contains ?tag2 ;} OPTIONAL { {?tag3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?contains2 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?tag2 ?contains2 ?tag3;} OPTIONAL{ {?tag4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag>;}{?contains3 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Includes>;} {?tag3 ?contains3 ?tag4;} } } } }

rdf:Description.Label: What are the line items this system has across the FYDP?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Funding ?GLTag (MAX(COALESCE(?FY13,0)) AS ?fy13) (MAX(COALESCE(?FY14,0)) AS ?fy14) (MAX(COALESCE(?FY15,0)) AS ?fy15) (MAX(COALESCE(?FY16,0)) AS ?fy16) (MAX(COALESCE(?FY17,0)) AS ?fy17) (MAX(COALESCE(?FY18,0)) AS ?fy18) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Funding ?GLTag ?FY13 ?FY14 ?FY15 ?FY16 ?FY17 ?FY18 WHERE { BIND(<@System-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/System@> AS ?System) {?System <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/System> ;} {?SystemBudgetGLItem <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY15>, ?Budget,0) AS ?FY15) } } UNION { SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?Funding ?GLTag ?FY13 ?FY14 ?FY15 ?FY16 ?FY17 ?FY18 WHERE { <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemServiceBudgetGLItem> ;} {?SystemService <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Has> ?SystemServiceBudgetGLItem} {?GLTag ;} {?SystemServiceBudgetGLItem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TaggedBy> ?GLTag} {?SystemServiceBudgetGLItem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/SelfReportCost> ?Budget ;} {?SystemServiceBudgetGLItem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/OccursIn> ?FYTag} BIND(IF(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY13>, ?Budget,0) AS ?FY13) BIND(IF(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY15>, ?Budget,0) AS ?FY15) BIND('' AS ?Funding) } } } GROUP BY ?System ?GLTag ?Funding

rdf:Description.Label: What are the system costs for a given organization?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT ?System ?FundingSource ?GLTag (max(coalesce(?FY13,0)) as ?fy13) (max(coalesce(?FY14,0)) as ?fy14) (max(coalesce(?FY15,0)) as ?fy15) (max(coalesce(?FY16,0)) as ?fy16) (max(coalesce(?FY17,0)) as ?fy17) (max(coalesce(?FY18,0)) as ?fy18)WHERE { BIND(<@Enterprise-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/Enterprise@> AS ?Enterprise) {?Enterprise <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/Enterprise> ;} {?Consists <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consists>;} {?System <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/System> ;} {?SystemBudgetGLItem <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SystemBudgetGLItem> ;} {?Has <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Has>;} {?GLTag <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/GLTag> ;}{?TaggedBy <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TaggedBy>;} {?FundedBy <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/FundedBy>;}{?FundingSource <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/FundingSource> ;} {?FYTag <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/FYTag> ;} {?System ?Has ?SystemBudgetGLItem}{?SystemBudgetGLItem ?TaggedBy ?GLTag}{?SystemBudgetGLItem ?FundedBy ?FundingSource} {?Enterprise ?Consists ?System} {?SystemBudgetGLItem <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/OldPrositeCost> ?Budget ;} {?SystemBudgetGLItem ?OccursIn ?FYTag} {?OccursIn <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/OccursIn>;} BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY13>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY13) BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY14>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY14) BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY16>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY16) BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY17>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY17) BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY18>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY18) BIND(if(?FYTag = <http://health.mil/ontologies/Concept/FYTag/FY15>, ?Budget,0) as ?FY15)} GROUP BY ?System ?GLTag ?FundingSource
